# Simple E-Commerce Store

This is a basic e-commerce web project built using HTML, CSS (Bootstrap), and JavaScript.  
It includes features such as:

- Product display
- Add to cart functionality
- Cart sidebar with total price
- Responsive layout using Bootstrap
- Styled UI with gradients and hover effects

## 👨‍💻 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3 (with Bootstrap 5)
- JavaScript

## 🛒 Features
- Display of 3 sample Nike products with images
- Add to Cart and Remove functionality
- Cart sidebar with total price calculation
- Interactive UI with hover effects and banners

